    "title": "京东开放平台食品饮料/粮油调味/休闲食品/水饮冲调类目资质标准",
    "followRuleId": "3712",
    "content": "<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff;\" border=\"0\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 228.264px; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; background: #c00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt;\" colspan=\"4\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 228.264px; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; background: #c00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.5pt;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm -5.45pt 0.0001pt -5.35pt; text-align: center; line-height: 21pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">一级类目</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 113.542px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; background: #c00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.5pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">行业资质</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; background: #c00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.5pt;\" colspan=\"2\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">特殊资质及要求</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 40.75pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 228.264px; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 40.75pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm -5.45pt 0.0001pt -5.35pt; text-align: center; line-height: 21pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">食品饮料/粮油调味/</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">休闲食品/水饮冲调</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 113.542px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 40.75pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">食品经营许可证：入驻开店公司的《食品经营许可证》，若当地销售预包装食品仅需备案，请上传备案回执；若当地销售预包装食品备案工作未开展，可提供情况说明。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">食品生产许可证（经营国产商品）：若入驻开店公司是生产商，且经营的产品全部为入驻开店公司生产，可提交《食品生产许可证》代替《食品经营许可证》。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 104.556px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 40.75pt;\">\n<p style=\"line-height: 21pt; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">若经营卡券，需提供以下资质：</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 21pt; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">须提供发卡方单用途预付卡备案的证明文件；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 21pt; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">发卡企业向备案机关提交的包含该入驻开店商家（售卡单位）的售卡企业清单及承诺函（入驻开店商家为发卡方无需提供此项）。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 111.028px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0cm; height: 40.75pt;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.3pt; line-height: 21pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">进口食品不强制要求提供商标注册证（旗舰店除外）。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.3pt; line-height: 21pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">报关单（经营进口商品）：近一年内的中华人民共和国海关进口货物报关单，报关单上应展现对应品牌名称及商品名称。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.3pt; line-height: 21pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">入境检验检疫（经营进口商品）：如有附页需提供完整，报关单与入境检疫需为近一年同一批次。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 228.264px; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt;\" colspan=\"4\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 0.05pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-indent: 7pt; line-height: 28px; background-color: white; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">旗舰店授权书模板：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #666666; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://helpcenter.jd.com/vender/issue/926-4279.html\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: blue;\">旗舰店授权书模板</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-indent: 7pt; line-height: 28px; background-color: white; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2. </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东开放平台各类目资费一览表：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #666666; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=638209647311982592&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: blue;\">京东开放平台类目资费规则</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.6pt; padding: 0px; color: #000000; white-space: normal; line-height: 28px; background-color: white; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3. </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">店铺命</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">名规则：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><a style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #666666; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2598\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: blue;\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2598</span></a></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"line-height: 21pt; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">附则</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 21pt; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东商家的行为，发生在本管理规则生效之日以前的，适用当时的规则。发生在本管理规则生效之日以后的，适用本规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 21pt; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东可根据平台运营情况随时调整本管理规则并以公告的形式向商家公示。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 21pt; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家应遵守国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件。对任何涉嫌违反国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件的行为，本规则已有规定的，适用于本规则。本规则尚无规定的，京东有权酌情处理。但京东对商家的处理不免除其应承担的法律责任。商家在京东的任何行为，应同时遵守与京东及其关联公司签订的各项协议。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 21pt; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; text-align: left; white-space: normal; font-size: 13.3333px; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">本规则标准于2025年9月15日修订，于2025年9月22日生效。</span></p>",
